## Package for Kamibot
### example

```
from pyKamibot.kamibot import Kamibot

kamibot = Kamibot('COM23', 57600)
# ---------------------------------------------------
# Turn on LED
# ---------------------------------------------------
kamibot.turn_led(200, 0, 0)
kamibot.delay(1)
kamibot.turn_led(0, 200, 0)
kamibot.delay(1)
kamibot.turn_led(0, 0, 200)
kamibot.delay(1)

# ---------------------------------------------------
# Move on mapboard
# ---------------------------------------------------
for i in range(0, 100):
    kamibot.turn_led(200, 0, 0)
    kamibot.delay(1)
    kamibot.turn_led(0, 200, 0)
    kamibot.delay(1)
```


